description: This file defines the interface for the BREE Module Container Object, including function prototypes for creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions related to the module container in a BSP runtime environment.

methods.name: BreeCreateModuleContainer
methods.description: Creates a new module container object given context handles.

methods.name: BreeMcoCreate
methods.description: Creates a module container object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: BreeMcoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified module container object.

methods.name: BreeMcoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects within the module container.
